{"tid":1543932,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［行動］每逢星期三四晚都係全民文宣日","createTime":"2019-09-05T11:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T16:49:35.000Z","uid":64810,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9144048cbf5d5a78fb1a0099dccd408da4019b1c","tid":1543932,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:17:26.000Z","msg":"經過動議<br />\n<br />\n動議 星期四晚做全民文宣日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1543542\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1543542</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我希望巴絲都要係星期三四晚出黎 貼文宣<br />\n同香港人講<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n清算黑警 刻不容緩<br />\n港人治港 理所當然<br />\n因果由國 容港治己<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點解要星期三四晚<br />\nA.因為星期一二係賽後檢討&amp;休息<br />\n星期五好大機會有集會<br />\n<br />\nQ.係咪剩係星期三四晚先貼文宣<br />\nA.唔係 每日都應該update 但鑑於有手足被藍絲打 所以我覺得有逼切要多人一齊出黎貼文宣<br />\n<br />\nQ.出黎有咩做<br />\nA.係非私人地方貼文宣 / 搞放映會 等，需要各位 保護貼緊文宣既手足<br />\n<br />\n認同請推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9eb160c440642cad36b1bf343a06f33545c6338","tid":1543932,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:18:17.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 出咗不反對啦！【9月6 反濫捕 抗威權 遮打集會】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1543083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1543083</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂]9.6遮打反濫暴抗威權集會 已獲批不反對通知書<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/agyFBwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/agyFBwU</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KTsuWvi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKTsuWvi.jpg&h=59781468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ud9tv0z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUd9tv0z.jpg&h=17d13451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wcJFfrO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwcJFfrO.jpg&h=7f9dd8d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TjeJddu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjeJddu.jpg&h=e690fd03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHcuNJL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHcuNJL.jpg&h=417a49e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d39cd33a9d0bdd23b8cc63be3d1a652043965b8","tid":1543932,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:18:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">時間為9-10pm</span>"},{"pid":"5ddfc11d5633ac8adb263ee8f190270b80bffc1b","tid":1543932,"uid":30201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:19:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">日日都係文宣日</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有消防巴話消防處講大話<br />\n其實真係開始成件事都好可疑<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">但大家依幾日不斷講嘅時候<br />\n有無諗過去做啲咩去prove呢？</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家幫手諗辦法攞831當晚cctv好嘛<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1543896\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1543896</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9d84145c8eaab7d9b842e605cbefabff0cb27898","tid":1543932,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8211de5fc556d4be9e053c7dcc45c3ab92f35025","tid":1543932,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45db5605ffd8fa20cc1448abe3c0d1c71bbb6bf5","tid":1543932,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caab9dc04c2193c693f3e89479b1bd4cad57